  "texts": [
    "The COVID-19 pandemic has further intensified existing mental health challenges globally.",
    "Specifically, the World Health Organization (WHO) reported a 26% rise in anxiety disorders and a 28% increase in major depression disorders within just one year of the pandemic 5.",
    "This escalating crisis underscores the urgent need for innovative approaches to mental health.",
    "The negative effects of poor mental health are far-reaching, with over 90% of people who die by suicide annually being diagnosed with a mental illness 6.",
    "These statistics point to the need to raise awareness of mental health in society and to take proactive early intervention and preventive measures."
  ],
